                                <a name="4467867762203669" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/Isty89fh3?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-03 13:02" date="1580706146000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4467867762203669:fromprofile"> 2月3日 13:02</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/6vtZb0" rel="nofollow">微博 weibo.com</a>            	                                            <span title="可于本微博右侧下拉菜单查看编辑记录">已编辑</span>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【人民来论：开工了，请管好自己】“不怕一万，就怕万一”。我们要时刻提醒自己：千万不能存在侥幸心理，认为单位的防范措施够丰富，该消毒的已消毒，该通风的已通风，就可以掉以轻心了。在这疫情防控的紧要关头，我们在岗的每个人，都应继续绷紧弦，比平时要更谨慎，也更自觉。<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%87%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%97%E5%87%BB%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%23&amp;from=default">#万众一心抗击疫情#</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/Isty89fh3" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4467867762203669:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4467867762203669&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%BD%A0%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E6%88%91%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E4%BD%A0%23&amp;from=default">#你守护大家我守护你#</a>【上海援鄂医生编战地礼仪绕口令】除夕，上海医生鲁立文和135名医护人员踏上驰援武汉的征程。他被队员戏称为<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%96%97%E9%98%9F%E9%87%8C%E7%9A%84%E7%AE%A1%E5%AE%B6%E5%A9%86%23&amp;from=default">#医疗队里的管家婆#</a>，总是时刻叮嘱大家要做好消毒工作。为此，还编了战地礼仪：不握手，不窜门，穿裤子不坐床边，讲话不交头接耳…<a target="_blank" render="ext" extra-data="type=atname" href="//weibo.com/n/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E7%BD%91%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E9%A2%91%E9%81%93?from=feed&amp;loc=at" usercard="name=人民网上海频道">@人民网上海频道</a> <a title="上海援鄂医生编出“战地礼仪”绕口令&nbsp;&nbsp;“要回家..." href="http://t.cn/A6PjTp8L" alt="http://t.cn/A6PjTp8L" action-type="feed_list_url" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="W_ficon ficon_cd_link">O</i>上海援鄂医生编出“战地礼仪”绕口令&nbsp;&nbsp;“要回家...</a> ​​​​                                            </div>

                                                                                                                        <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%23&amp;from=default">#新冠肺炎最新动态#</a>【<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%AD%A6%E6%B1%8926%E5%AE%B6%E5%AE%9A%E7%82%B9%E5%8C%BB%E9%99%A2%E7%97%85%E5%BA%8A%E5%89%A9%E4%BD%99%E6%83%85%E5%86%B5%23&amp;from=default">#武汉26家定点医院病床剩余情况#</a>】截至2月2日23:00，武汉市26家定点医院共开放床位7259，已用床位7332，空床位131。据<a target="_blank" render="ext" extra-data="type=atname" href="//weibo.com/n/%E9%95%BF%E6%B1%9F%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5?from=feed&amp;loc=at" usercard="name=长江日报">@长江日报</a> ，关于已用床位大于开放床位数的情况，是部分医院采取各种形式，竭尽所能、尽最大努力安排加床，形成已用床位数大于公布的开放床位数。（武汉卫健委） ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IstiIxiEl" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4467858207936517:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4467858207936517&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                                                                                                                        <a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%9C%80%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A8%E6%80%81%23&amp;from=default">#新冠肺炎最新动态#</a>【好消息！<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F%E5%B7%B2%E8%BF%9E%E7%BB%AD4%E5%A4%A9%E6%97%A0%E6%96%B0%E5%A2%9E%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B%23&amp;from=default">#西藏已连续4天无新增病例#</a>】截至2月2日24时，西藏自治区累计报告新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎确诊病例1例，重症病例0例，死亡病例0例，出院病例0例。目前，患者生命体征平稳，追踪到的密切接触者正在接受医学观察。因此，自1月29日确诊1例输入型新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎病例至2 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IsteJumQ9" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4467855737237641:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4467855737237641&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

            <div class="face"><a target="_blank" class="W_face_radius" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_pic" href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" title="人民网"><img usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/crop.24.3.657.657.1024/002uLDeXly8glmohn698dj60j60j6q3b02.jpg?KID=imgbed,tva&amp;Expires=1609338701&amp;ssig=TYRMCZnfR9" width="50" height="50" alt="人民网" class="W_face_radius"></a></div>

        <div class="WB_detail">

                    <a href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" target="_blank" class="W_f14 W_fb S_txt1" usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_name">人民网</a> <a target="_blank" href="//fuwu.biz.weibo.com"><i title="微博官方认证" class="W_icon icon_approve_co"></i></a><a title="微博会员" target="_blank" href="https://vip.weibo.com/personal?from=main" action-type="ignore_list" suda-uatrack="key=profile_head&amp;value=member_guest"><em class="W_icon icon_member7"></em></a></div>
                        <div class="WB_from S_txt2">
                                <a name="4467846124093527" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/IssZehaUD?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-03 11:36" date="1580700987000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4467846124093527:fromprofile"> 2月3日 11:36</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/6vtZb0" rel="nofollow">微博 weibo.com</a>            	            </div>

            <div class="PCD_user_b S_bg1" node-type="follow_recommend_box" style="display:none"></div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">

                                                                                                                        【广州<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%AD%E9%97%A8%E6%8A%8A%E6%89%8B%E6%B5%8B%E5%87%BA%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%A0%B8%E9%85%B8%23&amp;from=default">#患者家中门把手测出病毒核酸#</a> 提醒勤洗手！做好居家清洁！】日前，广州市疾控中心在疫情监测中，在一确诊患者家中门把手上发现新型冠状病毒的核酸，这是广州首次在外环境中发现。<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%BD%A0%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E6%88%91%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E4%BD%A0%23&amp;from=default">#你守护大家我守护你#</a> 专家提醒：手机屏幕、电脑键盘、水龙头等，都需要日常清洁。<a suda-uatrack="key=tblog_card&amp;value=click_title:4467842781014926:1034-video:1034%3A4467834139377695:page_100206_home:2286908003:4467842781014926:2286908003" title="广州日报的微博视频" href="http://t.cn/A6PjIzZ8" alt="http://t.cn/A6PjIzZ8" action-type="feed_list_url" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="W_ficon ficon_cd_video">L</i>广州日报的微博视频</a> <a target="_blank" render="ext" extra-data="type=atname" href="//weibo.com/n/%E5%B9%BF%E5%B7%9E%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5?from=feed&amp;loc=at" usercard="name=广州日报">@广州日报</a> ​​​​                                            </div>

                        <div class="WB_from S_txt2">
                                <a name="4467838687004608" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/IssNetody?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-03 11:06" date="1580699214000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4467838687004608:fromprofile"> 2月3日 11:06</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/6vtZb0" rel="nofollow">微博 weibo.com</a>            	                                            <span title="可于本微博右侧下拉菜单查看编辑记录">已编辑</span>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【商务部：<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%90%84%E5%9C%B0%E4%B8%8D%E5%BE%97%E9%9A%8F%E6%84%8F%E5%85%B3%E9%97%AD%E8%8F%9C%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%23&amp;from=default">#各地不得随意关闭菜市场#</a>等经营场所】商务部副部长王炳南3日在国务院新闻办举行的新闻发布会上说，已全面动员中小商贸企业复工开业，增加基本生活服务供给。各地面对疫情发展要及时充分评估，分级管控，不得随意关闭菜市场等经营场所，切实保障生活物资供应。<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%BD%A0%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E6%88%91%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E4%BD%A0%23&amp;from=default">#你守护大家我守护你#</a> ​​​​                                            </div>

                            <div class="WB_info">
                    <a href="//weibo.com/renminwang?refer_flag=1005055013_" target="_blank" class="W_f14 W_fb S_txt1" usercard="id=2286908003&amp;type=0&amp;refer_flag=1005055013_" suda-uatrack="key=noload_singlepage&amp;value=user_name">人民网</a> <a target="_blank" href="//fuwu.biz.weibo.com"><i title="微博官方认证" class="W_icon icon_approve_co"></i></a><a title="微博会员" target="_blank" href="https://vip.weibo.com/personal?from=main" action-type="ignore_list" suda-uatrack="key=profile_head&amp;value=member_guest"><em class="W_icon icon_member7"></em></a></div>
                        <div class="WB_from S_txt2">
                                <a name="4467834383902879" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/IssGignjF?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-03 10:49" date="1580698187000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4467834383902879:fromprofile"> 2月3日 10:49</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/6vtZb0" rel="nofollow">微博 weibo.com</a>            	            </div>

            <div class="PCD_user_b S_bg1" node-type="follow_recommend_box" style="display:none"></div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【工信部：<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E6%A0%B8%E9%85%B8%E6%A3%80%E6%B5%8B%E8%AF%95%E5%89%82%E4%BA%A7%E9%87%8F%E6%98%AF%E7%96%91%E4%BC%BC%E6%82%A3%E8%80%8540%E5%80%8D%23&amp;from=default">#核酸检测试剂产量是疑似患者40倍#</a>，已经基本满足要求】工信部总工程师田玉龙表示：2月1日，新型冠状病毒核酸检测试剂日产量已经达到了77.3万人份，是疑似患病者的40倍，已经基本满足要求。目前产能恢复值达到了百分之六七十，后期主要工作就是恢复产能。<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%87%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%97%E5%87%BB%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%23&amp;from=default">#万众一心抗击疫情#</a> <a target="_blank" render="ext" extra-data="type=atname" href="//weibo.com/n/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5?from=feed&amp;loc=at" usercard="name=人民日报">@人民日报</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IssGignjF" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4467834383902879:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4467834383902879&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">
                                                                                                                        【发改委回应口罩紧缺问题：<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%A8N95%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E5%BE%88%E5%A4%A7%23&amp;from=default">#医用N95口罩需求很大#</a>】解决口罩紧缺问题：①增加供应。正全力以赴增产、扩能，医用N95口罩需求很大，到昨晚已按一倍以上规模组织产能，准备原料，只要符合标准，企业可开足马力组织生产；②科学合理使用。要按需、按功能使用，避免过度使用。<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%87%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%97%E5%87%BB%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%23&amp;from=default">#万众一心抗击疫情#</a> <a target="_blank" render="ext" extra-data="type=atname" href="//weibo.com/n/%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E6%97%A5%E6%8A%A5?from=feed&amp;loc=at" usercard="name=人民日报">@人民日报</a> ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IssFe6MYx" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4467833721618233:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4467833721618233&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

                                                                                                                        【转发提醒！<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E8%BF%94%E7%A8%8B%E5%A4%8D%E5%B7%A5%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E7%94%B5%E6%A2%AF%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%23&amp;from=default">#返程复工如何避免电梯感染#</a>】门把手、按钮等风险高，不是因为病毒在上面存活长，而是因为频繁接触，交叉接触。应对策略：①适当增加消毒频次，以前一天一次现在一天多次；②用面巾纸、消毒纸巾隔开，手不直接碰。<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%BD%A0%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E6%88%91%E5%AE%88%E6%8A%A4%E4%BD%A0%23&amp;from=default">#你守护大家我守护你#</a> ​​​​                                            </div>

                        <div class="WB_from S_txt2">
                                <a name="4467828088522270" target="_blank" href="/2286908003/Issw8zL1Y?from=page_1002062286908003_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime" title="2020-02-03 10:24" date="1580696687000" class="S_txt2" node-type="feed_list_item_date" suda-data="key=tblog_home_new&amp;value=feed_time:4467828088522270:fromprofile"> 2月3日 10:24</a> 来自 <a class="S_txt2" suda-uatrack="key=profile_feed&amp;value=pubfrom_guest" action-type="app_source" target="_blank" href="https://app.weibo.com/t/feed/6vtZb0" rel="nofollow">微博 weibo.com</a>            	            </div>

                                                                                                                        【紧急！<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E5%AF%BB%E6%89%BE%E4%B9%98%E5%9D%90%E8%8F%B2%E5%BE%8B%E5%AE%BE%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%AA%E8%88%AA%E7%8F%AD%E4%B9%98%E5%AE%A2%23&amp;from=default">#寻找乘坐菲律宾多个航班乘客#</a>】菲律宾宿务太平洋航空公司在2月2日发布消息称，由于菲律宾出现的两例确诊病例都曾经在1月21日搭乘由其执飞的两个航班，因此需要追踪这两个航班的同行乘客。这两个航班的信息分别是：1月21日，由香港飞往菲律宾宿务的5J241（HONG KONG - CEBU）航班，以及1月21日 ​​​​...<a target="_blank" href="//weibo.com/2286908003/IssvQf2Bs" class="WB_text_opt" suda-uatrack="key=original_blog_unfold&amp;value=click_unfold:4467827903584930:2286908003" action-type="fl_unfold" action-data="mid=4467827903584930&amp;is_settop&amp;is_sethot&amp;is_setfanstop&amp;is_setyoudao&amp;is_from_ad=0">展开全文<i class="W_ficon ficon_arrow_down">c</i></a>                                            </div>

            <div class="WB_text W_f14" node-type="feed_list_content" nick-name="人民网">

                                                                                                                        【人民日报评论员：凝聚众志成城抗击疫情的磅礴力量】集中力量办大事是社会主义制度优越性的重要体现。中国人民是具有伟大团结精神的人民。疫情让人们在空间上保持距离，却让人们在心灵上贴得更近。<a target="_blank" render="ext" suda-uatrack="key=topic_click&amp;value=click_topic" class="a_topic" extra-data="type=topic" href="//s.weibo.com/weibo?q=%23%E4%B8%87%E4%BC%97%E4%B8%80%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%97%E5%87%BB%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%23&amp;from=default">#万众一心抗击疫情#</a>，哪里有疫情，哪里困难多，哪里就有四面援助、八方支持。<a suda-uatrack="key=tblog_card&amp;value=click_title:4467807088005495:1022-article:1022%3A2309354467807088672861:page_100206_home:2286908003:4467807088005495:2286908003" title="凝聚众志成城抗击疫情的磅礴力量" href="https://weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2309354467807088672861" alt="https://weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2309354467807088672861" action-type="feed_list_url" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><i class="W_ficon ficon_cd_longwb">°</i>凝聚众志成城抗击疫情的磅礴力量</a> ​​​​                                            </div>
                                                                <div class="WB_expand_media_box " style="display: none;" node-type="feed_list_media_disp"></div>
